      • pathDiverted

        void pathDiverted(DivertedVrpPath divertedPath,
                  double newEndTime)
        Vehicle changes its path. Just replaces the previous VrpPath with this one; this will work (if consistent) since (1) nobody (hopefully) caches a references to the original path, and (2) access to the link on the path is via index only (and not via an iterator or similar).

        Can be used for:
        • changing destination (while keeping the current task active)
        • stopping it as soon as possible (i.e. at the end of the current/next link)
        • random walk, roaming/cruising around
        • ...
